红酒品质的影响因素与分类预测¶

14307130391 AbstractThis report is based on a csv file which includes several physicochemical (inputs) variables and a sensory (the output) variable, quality, of red wine samples. The main tasks are regression and classification, and basic machine learning is used for classification. Through three basic models from desicion tree, svm and logistics regression, it is decided that the decision tree model fits the best. svm

ROCAUCAUC

(precision) = (TP)/(TP+FP)

(recall)=(TP)/(TP+FN)

F1 = 2/(+)

avg/total
